791-795 Bushwick Ave., at the N.W. corner of De Kalb Ave.  Also seen is 1201-1219 De Kalb Ave., west side, north from Bushwick Ave.  The trolley car is on De Kalb Ave.

September 9, 1932.

P.L. Sperr.
